  "title": "ADMINISTRATIVE OFFICER",
  "description": "<h3><u>ADMINISTRATIVE OFFICER</u></h3><p>•\tType, file and send all necessary correspondences directed by the PE or CM</p><p>•\tAnswer all inquiries requests or complaints received through the telephone and to keep proper records of such inquiries requests or complaints</p><p>•\tManage the booking of all facilities such as the BBQ pits, karaoke room, tennis courts etc.</p><p>•\tSet up a proper filing system to ensure smooth documentation and administration of the Corporation</p><p>•\tAssist the CM in the management of the petty cash</p><p>•\tKeep proper records of payments made by residents</p><p>•\tManage and maintain inventory of office stationery</p><p>•\tManage and arrange for the maintenance of all office equipment</p><p>•\tArrange all meetings as requested by the PE or CM and to prepare all necessary documents for such meetings</p><p></p>",
